Van Dijk: &ldquo;What a night. Fully deserved. It was amazing to be out there and playing with these guys. The goal was very special for me and my family.&quot;<br />
<br />
Van Dijk asked if it was a dream come true: &quot;Yeah definitely. Playing at Anfield for Liverpool is a dream for every player I think. To score a goal is even more special.&quot;
